Global Electromechanical Solenoid Valves Market Insights
Electromechanical Solenoid Valves Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 7.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Electromechanical Solenoid Valves Market Overview
The global Electromechanical Solenoid Valves market size was valued at USD 6.98 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% from 2025 to 2030. The increasing demand for automation in industries such as manufacturing, automotive, and oil & gas is driving the growth of the market. These valves are essential for controlling fluid flow in various applications, leading to a rise in their adoption across different sectors. The increasing focus on improving efficiency and reducing energy consumption has also supported the market's growth.

